les)%20from%20the%20Gaza%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20stages%2C%20DJs%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20a%20camping%20area%2C%20bars%20to%20cater%20for%20partygoers.%20Everything%20was%20in%20place%20for%20a%20weekend%20of%20dancing%20in%20the%20Negev%20desert.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20dawn%20broke%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20music%20suddenly%20stopped.%20It%20was%20around%206%3A30%20am.%20In%20the%20distance%2C%20noises%20that%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20party%20could%20be%20heard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%2C%20red%20alert%2C%20regroup%2C%26quot%3B%20warned%20the%20loudspeaker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESparks%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20explosion%20of%20rockets%20which%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-explainer-video-why-israels-iron-dome-struggled-to-defend-hamas-rockets-4473267%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintercepted%20by%20Iron%20Dome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Israel's%20air%20defence%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20the%20first%20signal%20of%20the%20horror%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEphraim%20Mordechayev%2C%2023%2C%20is%20a%20young%20soldier%20who%20had%20come%20to%20celebrate%20the%20weekend%2C%20which%20coincides%20with%20the%20Jewish%20Sabbath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20didn't%20comprehend%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP%20back%20in%20his%20apartment%20in%20the%20northern%20city%20of%20Or%20Akiva%2C%20still%20wearing%20the%20festival%20wristband.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20to%20panic%20but%20we%20were%20calm%2C%20we%20are%20used%20to%20this.%20We%20are%20just%20used%20to%20rockets%26quot%3B%20launched%20from%20the%20enclave%2C%20which%20has%20been%20under%20Israeli%20blockade%20since%20Hamas%20took%20control%20in%202007.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20man%20and%20his%20friends%20began%20to%20leave%20but%20soon%20realised%20that%20