eventh%20globally%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20SNE%20Research.%20Their%20combined%20market%20share%20of%20the%20global%20EV%20market%2C%20including%20electric%20and%20plug-in%20hybrid%20vehicles%2C%20has%20fallen%20to%204.3%25%20this%20year%20from%205.4%25%20in%202022%2C%20due%20to%20the%20strong%20growth%20of%20China's%20BYD%20Co.%2C%20the%20research%20group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHo%20Sung%20Song%20said%20Kia%20may%20introduce%20a%20compact%20model%20EV2%20in%20Europe.%20The%20European%20Union%20has%20started%20a%20probe%20into%20China's%20EV%20subsidies%2C%20which%20could%20result%20on%20tariffs%20being%20imposed%20on%20made-in-China%20cars%20and%20potentially%20benefit%20the%20Korean%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEV2%20is%20very%20unique%2C%20very%20important%20model%20for%20European%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEV2%20is%20very%20European%20style%20and%20it%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697115300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fg1jas7mo_kia-bed-ev-bloomberg_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcar-or-bedroom-with-a-fridge-see-kias-newest-ev-4475240%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kia%20Corp.%20unveiled%20a%20compact%20electric%20sport-utility%20vehicle%20and%20two%20concept%20EVs%20as%20it%20builds%20out%20a%20range%20of%20cheaper%20models%20to%20appeal%20to%20budget-conscious%20drivers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcar-or-bedroom-with-a-fridge-see-kias-newest-ev-4475240%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcar-or-bedroom-with-a-fridge-see-kias-newest