%20to%20enter%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20places%20in%20the%20world%2C%20to%20fight%20the%20Hamas%20group%20that%20launched%20a%20massive%20terror%20attack%20on%20Saturday.%20Over%201%2C200%20Israelis%20died%20in%20the%20terror%20attack%20and%201%2C500%20Hamas%20fighters%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20Israeli%20counterattack.%20At%20least%201%2C300%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20Strip%20have%20died%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20that%20flattened%20several%20large%20building%20into%20heaps%20of%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20today%20said%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20ground%20assault%20on%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20but%20the%20country's%20political%20leaders%20had%20not%20yet%20taken%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20waiting%20to%20see%20what%20our%20political%20leadership%20decides%20about%20a%20potential%20ground%20incursion%2C%26quot%3B%20army%20spokesman%20Richard%20Hecht%20told%20journalists%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Israelis%20roll%20into%20Gaza%20Strip%20with%20a%20mechanised%20infantry%20force%20along%20with%20air%20support%20from%20attack%20helicopters%2C%20a%20fierce%20form%20of%20urban%20warfare%20will%20break%20out%20on%20the%20narrow%20streets%20and%20lanes%20of%20the%20seaside%20area%2C%20where%20the%20population%20is%20a%20huge%205%2C500%20people%20per%20square%20kilometre%20(sqkm)%20compared%20to%20Israel's%20400%20people%20per%20sqkm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETactical%20challenges%20for%20Israeli%20ground%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EBuildings%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%20stand%20densely%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20space%20for%20such%20a%20huge%20population.%20The%20streets%20are%20narrow.%20It%20would%20be%20even%20more%20difficult%20for%20armoured%20personnel%20carriers%20(IFVs)%2C%20infantry%20fighting%20vehicles%20(IFVs)%20and%20tanks%20to%20navigate%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%20