cks-cold-foam-vanilla-sweet-cream-iced-coffee-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.25%20each%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20generate%20higher%20revenues%20for%20the%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrewer%20told%20investors%20in%20November%20that%20many%20customers%2C%20especially%20younger%20ones%2C%20opt%20to%20customize%20their%20cold%20drinks%20and%20add%20plant-based%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20TikTok%20frenzy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20demand%20for%20modifications%20may%20be%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-fast-food-restaurant-dining-habits-generations-money-spicy-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyounger%20people%20generally%20favor%20individualism%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20experts%20say.%20However%2C%20cold%20drinks%20with%20a%20long%20list%20of%20customizations%20are%20also%20more%20Instagram-worth%20for%20this%20social-media%20generation%2C%20with%20their%20clear%20plastic%20cups%20showing%20off%20the%20drinks'%20layers%2C%20creams%2C%20syrups%2C%20drizzles%2C%20and%20toppings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20these%20attractive%20drinks%20can%20go%20viral%20%E2%80%93%20the%20TikTok-inspired%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-tiktok-drink-iced-white-mocha-cold-foam-caramel-drizzle-2021-7%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eiced%20white%20mocha%2C%20for%20example%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20comes%20with%20vanilla%20sweet%20cream%20cold%20foam%20and%20extra%20caramel%20drizzle%20and%20saw%20baristas%20inundated%20with%20orders%20for%20%247%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20appeal%20of%20Starbucks%20doesn't%20stop%20there.%20The%20chain%20has%20changed%20its%20strategy%20to%20meet%20the%20changing%20needs%20of%20a%20tech-savvy%20generation%20by%20focusing%20on%20speed%20and%20convenience%20in%20ordering.%20Mobile%20orders%2C%20drive-thru%2C%20and%20delivery%20accounted%20for%2074%25%20of%20its%20second-quarter%20reven