the%20candidate%20responded%20right%20away.%20Bingo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222459%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22William%20Vanderbloemen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6526f5b16561dd877e77f570%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWilliam%20Vanderbloemen%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Vanderbloemen%20Search%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVanderbloemen%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Vanderbloemen%20Search%20Group%2C%20then%20decided%20the%20text-message%20test%20could%20be%20a%20good%20measure%20of%20whether%20a%20job%20candidate%20would%20mesh%20well%20with%20a%20client%20that%20has%20a%20move-fast%20culture.%20He%20compared%20it%20to%20pulling%20off%20a%20successful%20organ%20transplant%20by%20finding%20tissues%20that%20match%3A%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20you%20do%20things%20the%20way%20they%20do.%20Doesn't%20make%20it%20normal.%20Doesn't%20make%20it%20right.%20But%20you%20guys%20match%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitching%20the%20interview%20location%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVanderbloemen%20doesn't%20just%20rely%20on%20the%20text-message%20test.%20One%20time%2C%20while%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20he%20got%20turned%20around%20and%20realized%20he%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20coffee%20shop%20where%20he'd%20planned%20to%20meet%20a%20job%20candidate.%20So%20he%20contacted%20the%20man%20and%20asked%20whether%20they%20could%20meet%20somewhere%20else.%20The%20man%20responded%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20don't%20mind.%20I%20like%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVanderbloemen%20was%20impressed.%20Now%2C%20he'll%20sometimes%20change%20the%20location%20of%20an%20interview%2030%20minutes%20before%20it's%20set%20to%20take%20place%20to%20see%20how%20a%20candidate%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20something%20he%20does%20all%20the%20time%2C%20Vanderbloemen%20said.%20Some%20jobs%20don't%20require%20that%20kind%20of%20flexibil