re.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgujarat-election-kheda-public-flogging-hindu-muslim-communalism%5C%22%3Epublicly%20flogging%3C%2Fa%3E%20three%20Muslim%20men%20by%20tying%20them%20to%20a%20pole%20following%20their%20arrest%20on%20October%204%20last%20year.%20The%20arrested%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20pelting%20stones%20at%20a%20garba%20event%20during%20the%20Navaratri%20festival%20the%20previous%20day%20in%20Undhela%20village%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Kheda%20district.%20Last%20week%20when%20the%20issue%20reached%20the%20court%2C%20it%20framed%20charges%20against%20the%20errant%20police%20officers%20for%20contempt%20of%20court%20for%20violating%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20guidelines%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F235756%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ED.K.%20Basu%20vs%20the%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecase.%20The%20particular%20case%20laid%20down%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20during%20arrests%20and%20detentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fflogging-case-gujarat-cops-say-it-s-not-torture-101697049211359.html%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20policemen%20told%20the%20court%2C%20%E2%80%9CGiving%20three%20to%20six%20stick%20blows%20on%20buttocks%20of%20applicants%E2%80%A6%20though%20not%20proper%20and%20acceptable%2C%20it%20would%20not%20constitute%20custodial%20torture%20as%20to%20punish%20Respondent%20No%202%20(A.V.%20Parmar)%20for%20contempt%20of%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Parmar%2C%20who%20is%20an%20inspector%2C%20D.B.%20Kumavat%20(sub-inspector)%2C%20K.L.%20Dabhi%20(head%20constable)%2C%20and%20Raju%20Dabhi%20(constable)%2C%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20pay%20compensation%20to%20the%20victims%20in%20lieu%20of%20charges%20framed%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20policemen%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20Prakash%20Jani%2C%20also%20told%20the%20court%20that%20pronouncing%20them%20guilty%20and%20awarding%20them%20punishment%20would%20adversely%20affect%20their%20professional%20records%20given%20that%20they%20had%20already%20%E2%80%9Cdedicated%E2%80%9D%2010-15%20years%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20police%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20after%20hearing%20the%20submissions%20of%20the%20policemen%20sought%20a%20response%20from%20the%20Muslim%20men%20who%20brought%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20court.%20The%20next%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20will%20be%20on%20October%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%203%2C%202022%2C%20in%20the%20Undhela%20village%20in%20Kheda%20district%2C%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20members%20of%20the%20local%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20as%20the%20latter%20objected%20to%20a%20garba%20event%20being%20held%20near%20a%20mosque.%20The%20argument%20led%20to%20a%20violent%20clash%20and%20seven%20people%20were%20reportedly%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20of%20the%20case%20alleged%20that%20%E2%80%9Caround%20150%20people%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Muslim%20group%20attacked%20the%20planned%20garba%20venue%20late%20at%20night%20by%20allegedly%20pelting%20stones%2C%20injuring%20some%20policemen.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%2013%20men%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%20videos%20began%20making%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20police%20officers%2C%20later%20identified%20as%20being%20from%20the%20crime%20branch%2C%20tying%20the%20alleged%20attackers%20in%20the%20October%203%20violence%20to%20a%20poll%20and%20beating%20them%20with%20sticks%2C%20in%20full%20public%20view%20and%20amid%20cheers%20from%20the%20onlooking%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20sparking%20massive%20outrage%2C%20senior%20police%20officials%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20incident%20and%20against%20the%20policemen%20involved.%20Inspector%20A.V.%20Parmar%20and%20sub-inspector%20D.B.%20Kumavat%20were%20identified%20from%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVictims%20Jahirmiya%20Malek%20(62)%2C%20Maksudabanu%20Malek%20(45)%2C%20Sahadmiya%20Malek%20(23)%2C%20Sakilmiya%20Malek%20(24)%20and%20Shahidraja%20Malek%20(25)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkheda-flogging-police-notice%5C%22%3Emoved%20a%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20against%2015%20police%20personnel%20%E2%80%93%20the%20inspector%20general%20(IG)%2C%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%2C%20Kheda%3B%2010%20constables%20from%20the%20Matar%20police%20station%3B%20and%20three%20officers%20from%20the%20local%20crime%20branch%20(LCB).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20cited%C2%A0%3Ci%3ED.K.%20Basu%20versus%20the%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%20%3C%2Fi%3Ecase%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20top%20court%20laid%20down%20basic%20%E2%80%9Crequirements%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20police%20to%20follow%20during%20arrest%20and%20detention%20until%20legal%20provisions%20are%20made%20%E2%80%93%20accusing%20the%20policemen%20of%20flouting%20norms.%20They%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20initiate%20contempt%20of%20court%20proceedings%20against%20the%20policemen%20and%20also%20sought%20compensation%20be%20paid%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697101237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F05083127%2FScreenshot-2022-10-05-at-8.31.22-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkheda-flogging-hitting-people-on-buttocks-with-stick-not-torture-cops-tell-gujarat-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lawyer%20for%20the%20four%20accused%20policemen%20also%20told%20the%20court%20that%20pronouncing%20them%20guilty%20and%20awarding%20them%20punishment%20would%20affect%20their%20professional%20records%20as%20they%20had%20already%20'dedicated'%2010-15%20years%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20police%20department.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3