20the%20rising%20trade%20and%20current%20account%20deficit%2C%20which%20is%20now%20a%20stark%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0grapples%20with%20import-related%20challenges%2C%20it%20is%20not%20immune%20to%20export%20difficulties.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0has%20imposed%20export%20restrictions%2C%20particularly%20on%20agricultural%20products%2C%20which%20have%20led%20to%20lower%20exports%20realisation.%20On%20top%20of%20it%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0has%20a%20rising%20agricultural%20import%20bill%20primarily%20due%20to%20ever-burgeoning%20edible%20oil%20and%20pulses%20imports.%20The%20possible%20import%20of%20wheat%20from%20Russia%20could%20further%20stress%20our%20forex%20reserves%20and%20pressure%20the%20rupee.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20is%20subdued%20demand%20for%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20labour-intensive%20manufactured%20products%20like%20gems%20and%20jewellery%2C%20textiles%20and%20apparel%2C%20marine%20products%2C%20handicrafts%2C%20handlooms%20and%20leather%20products%2C%20in%20international%20markets%20resulting%20in%20lower%20inflow%20of%20foreign%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupply%20chain%20disruptions%20have%20added%20to%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20economic%20woes%2C%20causing%20a%20record%20rise%20in%20the%20import%20cost%20of%20essential%20goods%20including%20fuel%2C%20food%2C%20fertilisers%2C%20coal%20and%20critical%20minerals.%20Increased%20import%20of%20edible%20oil%20and%20pulses%20is%20driven%20by%20low%20domestic%20production%20and%20global%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20alternative%20uses%20of%20edible%20oil%20as%20biofuels%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20and%20deteriorating%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHigh-interest%20rates%20across%20leading%20economies%2C%20economic%20recessions%20and%20wavering%20consumer%20sentiment%20in%20countries%20like%20China%20and%20the%20US%20have%20l