0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fhimachal%2Fdespite-rain-disaster-himachal-pradesh-opens-shimla-green-belts-for-fresh-constructions-552457%3F_gl%3D1*4t6ixb*_ga*MTgxNDE0ODE3Mi4xNjk2ODIyMTA1%5C%22%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20move%20has%20come%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20torrential%20rains%20that%20caused%20unprecedented%20damage%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20in%20August.%20Worsening%20climate%20and%20constructions%20in%20the%20region%20often%20combine%20to%20increase%20the%20human%20cost%20of%20human%20disasters%20in%20the%20region.%20More%20interestingly%2C%20the%20government%20had%20enforced%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20construction%20activities%20in%20these%20belts%20in%20December%202000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2017%20green%20belts%2C%20spread%20over%20414.36%20hectares%2C%20were%20protected%20from%20constructions%20to%20save%20the%20deodar%20forests.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20the%20rains%20in%20August%20that%20were%20accompanied%20by%20landslides%20and%20flash%20floods%20led%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20nearly%201%2C000%20deodar%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20construction%20has%20only%20been%20allowed%20on%20land%20where%20there%20are%20no%20trees%20but%20the%20entire%20area%20is%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fhimachal%2Fdespite-rain-disaster-himachal-pradesh-opens-shimla-green-belts-for-fresh-constructions-552457%3F_gl%3D1*4t6ixb*_ga*MTgxNDE0ODE3Mi4xNjk2ODIyMTA1%5C%22%3Eheavily%20burdened%20with%20buildings%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20could%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20forests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20SDP%20on%20May%203%20followed%20by%20the%20Cabinet%E2%80%99s%20approval%20on%20June%2019.%20However%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20ordered%20that%20the%20notified%20SDP%20should%20be%20kept%