0her%20students%20about%20self-defence%2C%20good%20touch%20and%20bad%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20from%20her%20class%2C%20the%20initiative%20took%20new%20heights%20when%20the%20government%20school%20teacher%20started%20getting%20invitations%20from%20other%20schools%20and%20colleges%20in%20rural%20areas%20to%20impart%20self-defence%20training%20to%20their%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%202015%2C%20Asha%20has%20trained%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20girls%20from%20across%20Rajasthan.%20Of%20these%2C%20200%20students%20are%20girls%20with%20disabilities%20like%20visual%20impairment%2C%20speech%20impairment%2C%20and%20deafness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20her%20students%2C%20Monika%2C%20who%20is%20visually%20impaired%2C%20learned%20self-defence%20techniques%20from%20her%20last%20November.%20She%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20my%20childhood%2C%20my%20brother%20had%20to%20accompany%20me%20everywhere%20I%20go%2C%20be%20it%20to%20my%20friend%E2%80%99s%20home%20or%20daily%20to%20the%20school.%20Everyone%20feared%20for%20my%20safety%20as%20my%20disability%20made%20me%20more%20vulnerable.%20But%20now%2C%20my%20family%20does%20not%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20my%20safety.%20Today%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20I%20can%20knock%20down%20a%20perpetrator%20within%20minutes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20dedicates%20post-school%20hours%20and%20holidays%20to%20training%20sessions.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the