ball%20into%20attack%20positions.%20By%20using%20a%20dummy%2C%20we%20tell%20them%20if%20they%20sense%20danger%20from%20behind%20them%2C%20they%20then%20could%20hit%20them%20by%20bending%20their%20elbow%20in%20a%20similar%20manner%20when%20they%20brush%20their%20teeth.%20Or%20they%20could%20kick%20them%20like%20they%20would%20kick%20a%20football.%20When%20they%20hit%20the%20dummy%20themselves%2C%20they%20build%20confidence.%20With%20training%2C%20they%20learn%20how%20they%20could%20convert%20their%20body%20into%20a%20weapon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20tell%20my%20students%20to%20try%20negotiations%20first.%20%3Cem%3EPar%20agar%20baaton%20se%20kaam%20na%20chale%2C%20to%20laaton%20se%20kaam%20chalao.%20Aur%20laton%20pe%20aa%20jaaye%20to%20jhukna%20nahi%20hai.%20%3C%2Fem%3E(But%20when%20negotiations%20fail%20to%20work%2C%20hit%20them%20hard%2C%20and%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20that%2C%20then%20there%20should%20be%20no%20backing%20down)%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20such%20incident%2C%20Asha%20explains%20how%20she%20once%20saw%20a%20girl%20dragging%20a%20%3Cem%3Echhora%3C%2Fem%3E%20(boy)%20by%20his%20shirt%E2%80%99s%20collar%20and%20bringing%20him%20to%20her.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20told%20me%20how%20he%20passed%20comments%20on%20her.%20The%20guy%20apologised%20to%20us%20and%20even%20pledged%20not%20to%20flirt%20with%20any%20woman%20ever%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331727%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAsha%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20so%20satisfying%20to%20see%20this%20confidence%20among%20girls.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20women%20have%20come%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20empowered%20themselves.%20I%20have%20seen%20girls%20coming%20in%20trucks%20from%20villages%2030%20km%20away%20to%20learn%20self-defence%20from%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20work%2C%20Asha%20does%20not%20charge%20a%20penny.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20only%20%3Cem%3Eguru%20dakshina%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tuition%20fees%20of%20a%20teacher)%20from%20these%20students%20is%20that%20they%20pledge%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20their%20own%20safety%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20someone%20else%20like%20their%20father%20or%20brothers.%20Every%20woman%20must%20know%20safety%20rules%20and%20develop%20safety%20skills%20irrespective%20of%20their%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Asha%20was%20recognised%20at%20a%20State%20Level%20Teacher%20Award%20Ceremony%20by%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20for%20her%20work.%20She%20was%20also%20conferred%20the%20Ambedkar%20Mahila%20Puraskar%20Award%202023.%20This%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%20on%20September%205%2C%20she%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20recognition%2C%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20training%20young%20girls%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20is%20paramount%20for%20Asha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20this%20work%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20personal%20happiness.%20Now%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully%20knowing%20the%20girls%20I%20trained%20will%20be%20able%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20the%20humiliation%20that%20was%20once%20caused%20to%20one%20of%20my%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F1679310394CII2021Volume1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECrime%20In%20India%202021%20Volume%20I%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs)%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Asha%20Suman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696603084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1-1696597320.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alwar's%20Asha%20Suman%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20imparting%20self-defence%20skills%20to%20young%20girls.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20trained%2030%2C000%20girls%20across%20Rajasthan.%20This%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20she%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20National%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Award%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331721%2Frajasthan-government-school-teacher-trains-self-defense-to-girls-with-disabilities-national-award%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20Pilots%20Were%20Sued%20For%20Quitting.%20